{"tid":1012444,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 買左個電子磅唔識用","createTime":"2019-02-07T14:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T16:31:58.000Z","uid":130475,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f3a4b10104dd4e5374dcbb1e96534d978827cf","tid":1012444,"uid":130475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"前幾日買左個電子磅，多功能check 到體脂、骨質果種。今日得閒拎出來撚下，點知發現原來家母一早丟撚左個盒連說明書，而個磅的設計係好簡潔的，表面一個制都冇，得個底有粒制比你轉bl同kg，原全唔知點搞。我自認弱智，撚左幾個字撚埋右都搵唔到點先用到其他功能，請問有冇師兄有同一款磅知點用可以教下我呢個弱智，唔該晒各位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/225726_632bd11c86ac1dfcc3f9f25d40b8b7cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F225726_632bd11c86ac1dfcc3f9f25d40b8b7cd.png&h=fc6fe91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/07/225728_e8984942f14f0f2bb8185438b281795c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2F225728_e8984942f14f0f2bb8185438b281795c.png&h=a5069aa1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e4a4f061bfab64e39a4c6fdb569a6d5bafc31bd","tid":1012444,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63a55b7611229176d7c134a450244f005a97089c","tid":1012444,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"有冇上官網睇<br />\n佢底個粒長撳係咪有得reset<br />\n有冇試過連續撳幾下<br />\n有冇試過係磅上面企耐少少睇佢個moon有冇反應"},{"pid":"b3209d8d406c8648e68dce1b9324e6985ed5398c","tid":1012444,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"屌你個網上網乜柒資料都無<br />\n仲流過屌米磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7163bc348c74a653f81c739e66029babbd4de6a","tid":1012444,"uid":53845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"試下撳兩個箭咀中間嗰個掣"},{"pid":"dd16a20fb28c9c677993b95861c104a7fcf